<p>usually when new version reaches beta and/or prerelease stage, a lot of people write about what&#8217;s new. but they usually cover only the &#8220;big&#8221; changes. i&#8217;ll try to write about every new feature, so when it will be finally released, and somebody will be asked &#8220;whether we should upgrade to 8.4&#8243;, he will be able to simply point asker to <a href="http://www.depesz.com/index.php/tag/84/" rel="nofollow">http://www.depesz.com/index.php/tag/84/</a> to get a quick overview of what&#8217;s new <img src="http://www.depesz.com/wp-includes/images/smilies/icon_smile.gif" alt=":)" class="wp-smiley" /> </p>
